WizardTD

Class Monster

  • java.lang.Object
    • WizardTD.Monster
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Beetle, Gremlin, Worm

    public class Monster
extends java.lang.Object
    The Monster class represents a monster entity in the WizardTD game. Each monster has attributes such as type, health points (hp), speed, armour, mana gained upon being killed, and quantity. The class provides methods to get and set these attributes. Additionally, there are methods related to the monster's path and position that are intended to be overridden by subclasses.
